modName: Game of Thrones Daenerys Targaryen ECE CME SAVE
summary: A Skyrim CME save based of Daenerys Targaryen of GoT
descriptionHtml:
This is a character I created using enhanced character edit of everyone's favourite Khaleesi Daenerys Taragaryen. She will take up slot 4 of your CME saves (though this can be changed through renaming).

If you want your Khaleesi to look the exact same as mine you will need:
SG female texture renewal
SG hair 200+
Eyes if Perfection
UNP

If you want the famous Dany wedding dress you will need a mod called Yes Its a Dress that is not available on the nexus and will require a little bit of searching.

Thank You and Enjoy
author: TheWalker2002
